WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Camera tilts up; treetops fill the frame.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Leaves sway; the wind rustles softly.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Branches sketch patterns against the blue.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Sunlight filters through the moving canopy.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.000
A brief gust rises; shadows ripple and dance.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.000
The breeze eases; the sky opens wide.